available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section></div>\n\n<p>Element animateTransform służy do transformacji właściwości elementu takich jak skalowanie, obracanie, przechylanie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"użycie","title":"Użycie","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">Categories</th><td>Animation element</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th><td>Any number of the following elements, in any order:<br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#descriptive_elements\">Descriptive elements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>120<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuati